OL,3,CJoint mayor would 'discriminate'
OL,4,Cagainst Cornish people, says Labour MP
OL,6,FA Cornish Labour MP has warned he will
OL,7,Fvote against his Government's
OL,8,Fdevolution plans if it means the Duchy
OL,9,Fhas to merge with Devon to form a
OL,10,Fcombined authority and elect a joint
OL,11,Fmayor.
OL,13,FPerran Moon, the MP for Camborne and
OL,14,FRedruth, has said Labour's current
OL,15,Fproposal "discriminates against the
OL,16,Fpeople of Cornwall" because a change
OL,17,Fin local governance would conflict
OL,18,Fwith their National Minority Status.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
