OL,3,CJoint mayor would 'discriminate'
OL,4,Cagainst Cornish people, says Labour MP
OL,6,F"I have had enough of talk about
OL,7,FCornwall joining a Mayoral Combined
OL,8,FAuthority with Devon or anywhere else
OL,9,Fto the east of the Tamar, for that
OL,10,Fmatter," Mr Moon said.
OL,12,F"The currently proposed English
OL,13,FDevolution Bill discriminates against
OL,14,Fthe people of Cornwall, as a change in
OL,15,Four governance structure directly
OL,16,Fconflicts with our National Minority
OL,17,FStatus."
