OL,3,CJoint mayor would 'discriminate'
OL,4,Cagainst Cornish people, says Labour MP
OL,6,FAs they currently stand, Labour's
OL,7,Fplans would see all-remaining areas
OL,8,Fwith two tiers of local authority
OL,9,Feventually restructured into single-
OL,10,Ftier unitary bodies.
OL,12,FIn Devon for example, a combined
OL,13,Fcounty authority has already been
OL,14,Fgiven the green light, which includes
OL,15,Fthe merger of Devon County Council
OL,16,Fwith Torbay Council, and Devon's
OL,17,Fdistrict, city and borough councils.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
