OL,3,CJoint mayor would 'discriminate'
OL,4,Cagainst Cornish people, says Labour MP
OL,6,FThe plans would also see unitary
OL,7,Fauthorities join up with those in
OL,8,Fneighbouring areas to form so-called
OL,9,F'super councils', run by elected
OL,10,Fmayors with control over policy areas
OL,11,Fsuch as transport, housing and skills
OL,12,Fbudgets.
OL,14,FThe idea is that these combined
OL,15,Fauthorities would represent a
OL,16,Fpopulation size of around 1.5million
OL,17,For above.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
