OL,3,CJoint mayor would 'discriminate'
OL,4,Cagainst Cornish people, says Labour MP
OL,6,FLabour is realising that different
OL,7,Fparts of the country have very
OL,8,Fdifferent idea about what successful
OL,9,Fdevolution looks like.
OL,11,FTo a number of MPs in Cornwall, that
OL,12,Fdoesn't mean joining with Devon. It
OL,13,Fmeans a bespoke 'deal' for the Duchy
OL,14,Fthat comes with its own promises of
OL,15,Flocal power and investment.
OL,17,FAngela Rayner previously told ITV West
OL,18,FCountry that she's "enticing" them to
OL,19,Fembrace the mayoral model, but not
OL,20,Fforcing, though it's still not clear
OL,21,Fwhat that really means.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
