OL,3,CJoint mayor would 'discriminate'
OL,4,Cagainst Cornish people, says Labour MP
OL,6,FThis week, the Camborne and Redruth MP
OL,7,Fasked one of Ms Rayner's deputies for
OL,8,Fclarity.
OL,10,FCornwall is "desperate to access the
OL,11,Fhighest level of devolution," Mr Moon
OL,12,Fsaid, before adding: "Cornwall cannot
OL,13,Fand will not join a mayoral combined
OL,14,Fauthority."
OL,16,FJim McMahon, the minister responsible
OL,17,Ffor devolution, said: "We absolutely
OL,18,Funderstand and respect, and are
OL,19,Finvested in, the Cornish identity.
