OL,3,CJoint mayor would 'discriminate'
OL,4,Cagainst Cornish people, says Labour MP
OL,6,F"But we also need to make sure the
OL,7,Fdevolution agenda moves on at pace and
OL,8,Fthat every part of England can realise
OL,9,Ftheir full potential."
OL,11,FThe rhetoric from Cornish MPs on
OL,12,Fdevolution has stepped up a gear, and
OL,13,Fwill no doubt continue to do so.
