OL,3,CJoint mayor would 'discriminate'
OL,4,Cagainst Cornish people, says Labour MP
OL,6,F"A Cornwall-only devolution deal is
OL,7,Fthe right deal for Cornwall and I will
OL,8,Fbe significantly increasing the
OL,9,Fprofile of this issue in national
OL,10,Fmedia over the summer until we get the
OL,11,Fdevolution deal that respects our
OL,12,Funique status," Mr Moon told
OL,13,Fconstituents in a post on Facebook.
OL,15,F"If changes aren't made to the English
OL,16,FDevolution Bill or we cannot agree a
OL,17,FCornwall-only deal before we are asked
OL,18,Fto vote on the Bill, I WILL vote
OL,19,Fagainst it."
